subtitleNullable: National Stock Exchange of India - Yahoo Finance equivalent ticker codes
descriptionNullable:
### Context

National Stock Exchange (NSE) ticker (stock) names and their Yahoo Finance equivalent ticker codes.


### Content

I have added a CSV file that contains all of the NSE ticker names and their Yahoo Finance equivalent ticker codes as on January 15th, 2021


### Acknowledgements

NSE India 


### Inspiration

Data can be used for various machine learning techniques to evaluate stock performance or to create best stock portfolios.
